{"id": 1296, "genre": 1001, "title": "你受不了哪些简单粗暴的建议？", "description": "世界和平还没实现都是因为你们思路不够开阔啊。（题图来自：Rafael Alvarez）", "record_count": 4469, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161028142712IZNnAHxFw9PM574T.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-29T17:00:22Z", "options": [{"id": 128769, "content": "大过年的...", "image": "img/option/option/20161031022659fhW9NkQyLT0bXMdZ", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567669}, {"id": 128514, "content": "既来之者安置", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809813}, {"id": 128770, "content": "你这人怎么开不起玩笑呢?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612449}, {"id": 129538, "content": "“蓝瘦香菇”听到有人说这个就神烦，都不会好好说话了？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807479}, {"id": 128771, "content": "“我觉得还好吧”------向人诉苦寻求认同得到的回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814173}, {"id": 128517, "content": "要学会宽容，平静看待事情，要学会调节", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787250}, {"id": 128773, "content": "“我这人就这样，你能忍的了就忍，忍不了我也没办法” ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803796}, {"id": 128518, "content": "学学别人家的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787250}, {"id": 128774, "content": "过了这个年纪就没得挑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755623}, {"id": 128519, "content": "为什么你不学好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787250}, {"id": 128775, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812160}, {"id": 128776, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812160}, {"id": 128777, "content": "努力就会成功，坚持就是胜利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751658}, {"id": 128778, "content": "你顺便嘛～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741174}, {"id": 128523, "content": "反正你脸皮厚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762342}, {"id": 128779, "content": "你不小了，该找个人嫁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758457}, {"id": 128524, "content": "宝贝儿，好啦好啦…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806323}, {"id": 128780, "content": "你岁数不小了，马上30，该找个人嫁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758457}, {"id": 128525, "content": "你就是对的，我说的绝对是错的，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627204}, {"id": 128781, "content": "这里有个问题啊\n哪里？\n这里，应该xxxxxxx做才是\n傻哟，你改一下就行啦\n?这是你给的数据有问题，所以就理所当然让发现的我来改？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802484}, {"id": 128526, "content": "我这人就是刀子嘴豆腐心！呵呵……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806574}, {"id": 128782, "content": "同性恋者都是精神不正常的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815311}, {"id": 128527, "content": "以前不都是你做的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681349}, {"id": 128783, "content": "女孩子没必要上大学！这种典型的大男子主义，听完果断回复：你养我！！！??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781434}, {"id": 128528, "content": "我以为你不参加呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814635}, {"id": 128784, "content": "我比你小 你要让着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662598}, {"id": 128529, "content": "没得事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154500}, {"id": 128785, "content": "一切都会好起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815129}, {"id": 128530, "content": "我讲话就是这么直，你告诉我怎么改嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748956}, {"id": 128786, "content": "你开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788799}, {"id": 128531, "content": "这得凭自己感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 134932, "content": "好生孩子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831380}, {"id": 136980, "content": "不喜欢她这样直说不就完了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 128788, "content": "客户直言你设计的很丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632962}, {"id": 129300, "content": "嗯    哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817805}, {"id": 136981, "content": "来大姨妈有什么不能吃凉的啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 128533, "content": "我无所谓 看你", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 128789, "content": "你多大年纪了还追星，我喜欢明星怎么啦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773654}, {"id": 129046, "content": "要学会适应，学会改变自己。事实上，我正是因为某种原因不愿意改变自己才引来的麻烦~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815997}, {"id": 133911, "content": "想瘦啊？割肉去啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833441}, {"id": 128791, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797801}, {"id": 132889, "content": "多喝水?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783500}, {"id": 134169, "content": "喜欢就买，不行就分，多喝热水，重启试试。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834885}, {"id": 129049, "content": "随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726815}, {"id": 129561, "content": "看开点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511564}, {"id": 128794, "content": "加油_(:3」∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769244}, {"id": 128539, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246132}, {"id": 128795, "content": "痛经都是自己作出来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815360}, {"id": 128540, "content": "反正就这样了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777982}, {"id": 128796, "content": "多喝热水，关机重启，不行就分", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}]}